The four dinobots burst out of the predacon base. As they were running away the toxic gas they breathed in started to make them sick. And the autoguns kept fireing upon them. But they stumbled on. Trying to get away from the predacons. "Where are those freaking maximal reinforcements I called for!!" Triceradon screamed.
